Document [3] (Title: She's Leaving Home (Grey's Anatomy)) She's Leaving Home (Grey's Anatomy) "She's Leaving Home" is the 22nd and 23rd episode of the eleventh season of the American television medical drama "Grey's Anatomy", and the 242nd and 243rd episode overall. The episodes aired on April 30, 2015 on ABC in the United States. The episodes were written by Stacy McKee and directed by Chris Hayden. On its initial airing it was watched by 8.74 million viewers. The two-hour episode serves as a tribute to the death of Derek Shepherd, the show's male lead played by Patrick Dempsey, who died in a car accident in the previous episode.
